@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vdcvra(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (tmp + wp.exp((v1 + 1.00 * v0 + 0.74)))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.58) + (v1 + v2))
    v1 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.12 + v2 + 0.52) * v0))
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.84)) * ((v0 + 0.86 / tmp + 0.66) * v2))
    data[tid] = v0
